# group `systemcapi` 

Define API for interacting with system level intrinsics.

## Summary

 Members                        | Descriptions                                
--------------------------------|---------------------------------------------
`public void `[`eosio_assert`](#group__systemcapi_1ga8566f3999bfc932b2190d05e97abbe1f)`(uint32_t test,const char * cstr)`            | Aborts processing of this action and unwinds all pending changes.
`public void `[`eosio_exit`](#group__systemcapi_1gae6b0de62b1edad98f29873b53f75dda0)`(int32_t code)`            | This method will abort execution of wasm without failing the contract. This is used to bypass all cleanup / destructors that would normally be called.
