## Members

#### `public void `[`eosio_assert`](#group__systemcapi_1ga8566f3999bfc932b2190d05e97abbe1f)`(uint32_t test,const char * cstr)` 

Aborts processing of this action and unwinds all pending changes.

Aborts processing of this action and unwinds all pending changes if the test condition is true 
#### Parameters
* `test` - 0 to abort, 1 to ignore 

* `cstr` - a null terminated action to explain the reason for failure

#### `public void `[`eosio_exit`](#group__systemcapi_1gae6b0de62b1edad98f29873b53f75dda0)`(int32_t code)` 

This method will abort execution of wasm without failing the contract. This is used to bypass all cleanup / destructors that would normally be called.

#### `public `[`time`](#group__types_1ga44479e2657d126b44ca53d30c3e670d8)` `[`now`](#group__systemcapi_1ga5eef43c9589d6ef54a0ece1dda5e0ffe)`()` 

Get time of the last accepted block.

Returns the time in seconds from 1970 of the last accepted block (not the block including this action) 
#### Returns
time in seconds from 1970 of the last accepted block

